description:
Proper Japanese Title: 遊☆戯☆王 テンス　アニバーサリー　アニメーション　ブック

This release was both a celebration of the past and a promotion for the 3-D movie, Bonds Beyond Time, which was released two days after the book. Note, it's celebrating the 10th anniversary not of the franchise (which began as a manga in 1996) or of it first being adapted into an anime (which was done by Toei in 1998) but the second anime series (which was hugely successful and resulted in numerous spin-offs) that began in 2000.
name: Yu-Gi-Oh! 10th Anniversary Animation Book
